{"tid":972247,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果》：夏志誠未獲北京「祝福」　教廷敲定湯漢署理教區主教","createTime":"2019-01-07T09:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T10:33:39.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f839e4e9ea4c6c99710553ef2f9a0418ea2627a7","tid":972247,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區前主教楊鳴章上周四（3日）病逝，主教署任人選惹關注。《蘋果日報》今日引述消息稱，呼聲最高的輔理主教夏志誠由於敢言，一直不獲北京「祝福」，教廷兩日前敲定由榮休主教湯漢樞機出任署理主教。<br />\n<br />\n夏志誠的作風較其他署理主教人選開明，願意開腔談民主，聲援「佔中三子」，過往亦多次出席六四燭光晚會。日前被問及是否擔心政治立場令他無法獲得教區主教任命，他表示不擔心，因為每個人都有自己的政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n湯漢於2009年就任香港教區主教，2012年獲教宗本篤十六世擢陞為樞機，去年8月1日榮休，由楊鳴章接任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/266896/%E3%80%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%8F%E5%BF%97%E8%AA%A0%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F%e3%80%80%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E6%B9%AF%E6%BC%A2%E7%BD%B2/?fbclid=IwAR2uST5NIz2RE21gW04nlqBBKu7l_edxA_46yC4QFiDRxsWnG3lbXvxVuwY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F266896%2F%25E3%2580%258A%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E3%2580%258B%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25A4%258F%25E5%25BF%2597%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%25A6%258F%25e3%2580%2580%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25BB%25B7%25E6%2595%25B2%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%25BD%25B2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2uST5NIz2RE21gW04nlqBBKu7l_edxA_46yC4QFiDRxsWnG3lbXvxVuwY&d=MmsljSwmbRLmMNnuRoW8H%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=08f1c400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/266896/%E3%80%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%8F%E5%BF%97%E8%AA%A0%E6%9C%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%A5%9D%E7%A6%8F%e3%80%80%E6%95%99%E5%BB%B7%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E6%B9%AF%E6%BC%A2%E7%BD%B2/?fbclid=IwAR2uST5NIz2RE21gW04nlqBBKu7l_edxA_46yC4QFiDRxsWnG3lbXvxVuwY</a>"},{"pid":"4b3b995512473289091da367decaa807f8dd00c0","tid":972247,"uid":14918,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"